  "title": "Privacy and Confidentiality",
  "description": "The hospital must protect patient privacy and maintain confidentiality of patient information in accordance with ethical standards and applicable laws. This includes safeguarding medical records, ensuring private consultations, restricting disclosure of patient information, and implementing measures to prevent unauthorized access to patient data.",
